{"tid":1114113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專業美術用品公司宣布結業　香港藝術學生必到之地","createTime":"2019-04-18T09:39:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T08:08:43.000Z","uid":136738,"like":149,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"e684cfe61ff4e4df7e7220002cbb2f6b1a3ce573","tid":1114113,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"位於旺角弼街的專業美術用品公司（Art Supplies）多年來一直是香港讀藝術、設計學生的必到之地。該美術用品店今早宣布，經過 30 多年經營後，將於今年 4 月 30 日結業。<br />\n<br />\n專業美術用品公司今早在 facebook 專頁宣布 4 月 30 日的結業消息，指「承蒙新知舊雨一直關愛，能和大家走過 30 多個年頭，是我們的最大榮幸」，又祝顧客於往後日子「繼續熱愛藝術，有緣再會」。<br />\n<br />\n消息隨即引來網民頗大迴響，不足一小時，已有逾 200 人分享該帖。本地漫畫家江記在網上分享消息並感慨：「有啲大鑊啊咁，佢有無 online store？」又稱自己至今仍用紙筆作畫。另一漫畫家 Cuson 在分享消息時亦慨嘆：「嗚嗚嗚&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n而 3 月初專業美術用品公司已宣布，由 3 月 9 日到 4 月 30 日，全店貨品 7 折，結果這優惠期結束亦是該店結業的日子。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd5218ec0f89eca62592b4e926daf4b16dd21f2","tid":1114113,"uid":16676,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"Apple pen "},{"pid":"cd26e8e87427b47b210c6e3f4938aebe1e8ab904","tid":1114113,"uid":136738,"like":1,"dislike":24,"score":-23,"quote":{"pid":"ecd5218ec0f89eca62592b4e926daf4b16dd21f2","tid":1114113,"uid":16676,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"Apple pen "},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:42:56.000Z","msg":"咩2c=="},{"pid":"8b114f89742e810c8827d1f2f4989408fb15f40f","tid":1114113,"uid":48358,"like":50,"dislike":14,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T09:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01GfFkH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01GfFkH.png&h=126a7f1a&s={SIZE}\" />"